xternal\">Please refer to our guide to project costs for further information.</a></p>','\0','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,36,454,NULL,'GENERAL',NULL),(1060,'','Please provide a breakdown of the materials you expect to use during the project','','','Materials','Materials',2,NULL,36,454,NULL,'COST',NULL),(1061,'','<p>You can claim the usage costs of capital assets you will buy for, or use on, your project.</p>','\0','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,36,455,NULL,'GENERAL',NULL),(1062,'','Please provide a breakdown of the capital items you will buy and/or use for the project.','','','Capital Usage','Capital items',2,NULL,36,455,NULL,'COST',NULL),(1063,'','<p>You can subcontract work if you dont have the expertise in your project team. You can also subcontract if it is cheaper than developing your skills in-house.</p>','\0','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,36,456,NULL,'GENERAL',NULL),(1064,'','Please provide details of any work that you expect to subcontract for your project.','','','Sub-contracting costs','Sub-contracts',2,NULL,36,456,NULL,'COST',NULL),(1065,'','<p>You should include travel and subsistence costs that relate to this project. </p>','\0','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,36,457,NULL,'GENERAL',NULL),(1066,'',NULL,'','','Travel and subsistence',NULL,2,NULL,36,457,NULL,'COST',NULL),(1067,'','<p>Please provide details of any project costs which cannot be covered by the other cost categories.</p>','\0','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,36,458,NULL,'GENERAL',NULL),(1068,'','Please note that legal or project audit and accountancy fees are not eligible and should not be included as an \'other cost. Patent filing costs of new IP relating to the project are limited to 7,500 for SME applicants only.  Please provide estimates of other costs that do not fit within any other cost headings.','','','Other costs','Other costs',2,NULL,36,458,NULL,'COST',NULL),(1069,'\0','To determine the level of funding you are eligible to receive please provide your business size using the <a href=\"http://ec.europa.eu/growth/smes/business-friendly-environment/sme-definition/index_en.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">EU definition (opens in a new window)</a> for guidance.','','','Size','Business size',18,NULL,36,459,NULL,'GENERAL',NULL),(1070,'\0','Please enter the funding level that you would like to apply for in this application','','','Funding level','Funding level',19,NULL,36,460,NULL,'GENERAL',NULL),(1071,'\0','Please tell us if you have applied for, or received any other public sector funding for this project. This information is important as other public sector support counts as part of the funding you can receive for your project.','','','Other funding','Other funding',20,NULL,36,460,NULL,'COST',NULL),(1072,'\0','','\0','\0',NULL,NULL,16,NULL,36,461,NULL,'GENERAL',NULL),(1073,'',NULL,'\0','\0','FINANCE_SUMMARY_INDICATOR_STRING',NULL,17,NULL,36,461,NULL,'GENERAL',NULL);
